# Scott's ~/.gitignore_global excludes "CLAUDE.md" (no-slash + macOS case-insensitive),
# which swallows ANY claude.md at any depth. We WANT the root CLAUDE.md ignored (internal,
# not shipped publicly), but the host doc docs/hosts/claude.md must stay tracked — so scope
# the re-include to that one path only, rather than a blanket !CLAUDE.md.
!docs/hosts/claude.md

